I"/<h2 id="glass의-색감">Glass의 색감</h2>
<ul>
  <li><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=a16EGZreJlM">How to Create A Glass Material</a></li>
</ul>

<p>MaterialDomain = Surface; <br />
BlendMode = Translucent; <br />
LightingMode = SurfaceTranslucencyVolume;</p>

<p>BaseColor = float4(0.005, 0.001, 0.00848, 0.996); <br />
Metalic = 0.1; <br />
Soecykar = 26; <br />
Roughness = 0.1; <br />
Alpha = Fresnel_function(Power = 1.5); <br />
Opacity = Lerp (0.008, 0.9, Alpha); <br />
Replaction = Lerp (1.05, 0.95, Alpha);</p>

<ul>
  <li><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=527ZcxYnf_s">UE4 Tutorial: Milky Glass</a></li>
</ul>

<p>Translucent material은 scene color texture를 가져올 수 있습니다.
SpiralBlur - SceneTexture를 사용할 수 있습니다. Opacity와 Emmisive에 올바른 값을 연결하면 작동합니다.</p>

